children.name: doseTrimesterExposureEndJ
children.description:
Calculate End of Exposure Trimester : CASE: [Max (Pregnancy Outcome Date)- Date of LMP]/7
 a. < 0: Pre Conception
 b. >= 0 AND < 14 1st
 c. >= 14 AND < 28 2nd
 d. >= 28 AND < 43 3rd
 e. >= 43 Post Conception
 ELSE
 i. calculate End of Exposure Trimester : CASE: Therapy Stop Date - Date of LMP/7
 a. < 0 Pre Conception
 b. >= 0 AND < 14 1st
 c. >= 14 AND < 28 2nd
 d. >= 28 AND < 43 3rd
 e. >=4 Post Conception

children.name: doseTrimesterExposureEnd
children.description:
Calculate End of Exposure Trimester : CASE: [Max (Pregnancy Outcome Date)- Date of LMP]/7
 a. < 0: Pre Conception
 b. >= 0 AND < 14 1st
 c. >= 14 AND < 28 2nd
 d. >= 28 AND < 43 3rd
 e. >= 43 Post Conception
 ELSE
 i. calculate End of Exposure Trimester : CASE: Therapy Stop Date - Date of LMP/7
 a. < 0 Pre Conception
 b. >= 0 AND < 14 1st
 c. >= 14 AND < 28 2nd
 d. >= 28 AND < 43 3rd
 e. >=4 Post Conception

children.name: dvPregnancyGestAgeDays
children.description:
Pregnancy Outcome Date - Date of LMP

If any of the following conditions are met, the system must display <blank> instead of performing the calculation:
- Pregnancy Outcome Date is unknown
- Date of LMP is unknown/an estimated date

children.name: dppiPatGestAgeDose3Days
children.description:
The report shall use below logic to calculate the Trimester:
 1. If Pregnancy Outcome < = Date of LMP AND Date of LMP is fully known then NULL
 2. If Latest Pregnancy Outcome Date < All Therapy Start Date of Dose 3 across all the POIs in the case AND all Therapy Start date of Dose 3 are fully known, then NULL.
 3. If Therapy Start Date of Dose 3 is Unk/Partial Date , Print Unk
 4. If Date of LMP is Unk/Partial Date, Print Unk
 5. If some Therapy Start Dates are partial dates and all the fully known Therapy Start dates of Dose 4 > Latest Pregnancy Outcome Date
 6. If Pregnancy Outcome is Unknown OR Therapy Start Date of Dose 3 Tab < Latest Pregnancy Outcome Date then calculate Trimester as:
 Therapy Start Date - Date of LMP] /7
 a. < 0: Pre Conception
 b. >= 0 AND < 14: 1st
 c. >= 14 AND < 28: 2nd
 d. >= 28 AND < 43: 3rd
 e. >= 43: Post
 7. For Therapy Start Date of Dose 3 Tab > Latest Pregnancy Outcome Date AND at least one fully known Therapy Start Date < Latest Pregnancy Outcome Date: Post
